IFB INDUSTRIES LTP: Rs 368.45
Action: BUY on dips
Targets: Rs 374 / Rs 377.7
Stop-loss: Rs 360
Comment: Stock has taken support around Rs 350.
Volumes have moved above the 10 day average.
Momentum oscillators are supporting continuation of uptrend and are coming off the oversold region.
MACD is about to cross the signal line.
NATCO PHARMA LTP: Rs 466.5
Action: Buy on declines
Targets: Rs 473.5 / Rs 480
Stop-loss: Rs 452
Comment: The momentum indicators are supporting further upside.
The stock has found some support around the 50% fibonacci retracement level and has bounced back.
AVANTI FEEDS LTP: Rs 466.9
Action: BUY on dips
Targets: Rs 474 / Rs 482
Stop-loss: Rs 456
Comment: Momentum oscillators are showing continuation of the reversal that has happened from the middle bollinger band level of Rs 440 and is expected to move towards the upper band of Rs 488.
Volumes have jump above the 10 day average.
